headline: New railroad debuts in Louisville, offering West Coast connections. Here's what we know

headline: Is Union Pacific Trump ballroom donation Vena’s  merger knockout punch?
summary: Union Pacific has made a donation to help fund President Trump’s White House ballroom, ostensibly to help win regulatory approval of its $85 billion merger with Norfolk Southern.
